\ls3\ilvl0\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can I just suggest that you and I coming together every week for 60 minutes and singing songs and maybe even raising your hand and maybe even feeling closer to God isn\'92t what God is ultimately looking for?\
