\ls3\ilvl1
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t talk to me if you have been treating wife badly\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t talk to me until you fix it with someone else\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\b \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Worship is truly understanding God\'92s mercy on you to the point that it affects your actions towards others.\
